WEBVTT

01:27.420 --> 01:31.880
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.190 --> 01:34.880
[Episode 13]

01:43.560 --> 01:44.060
Jiale!

01:49.039 --> 01:50.640
What's wrong? Why are you pouting?

01:50.640 --> 01:51.570
Are you unhappy?

01:52.680 --> 01:54.880
I want to go back to my mom's place today.

01:55.590 --> 01:56.150
Why?

01:58.940 --> 02:04.720
[The First Military Rule Came Into Being]

01:59.479 --> 02:01.000
Your mom's been busy recently,

02:01.000 --> 02:03.930
so she asked you to stay in my place
for a few more days.

02:04.590 --> 02:05.190
And you...

02:05.310 --> 02:07.480
Didn't you say you wanted to play squash?

02:06.120 --> 02:11.300
[The Story of Half a Blanket]

02:07.480 --> 02:09.610
I've already booked the venue for you.

02:12.580 --> 02:14.080
I saw that video.

02:16.420 --> 02:17.420
How did you see it?

02:22.910 --> 02:24.770
You're worried about her, right?

02:30.630 --> 02:31.630
She's very brave.

02:32.280 --> 02:34.000
She totally slayed this.

02:35.320 --> 02:36.579
I mean, she's amazing.

02:38.300 --> 02:40.230
You didn't know about this before?

02:42.520 --> 02:43.200
Nope.

02:44.079 --> 02:44.540
Well,

02:44.590 --> 02:45.960
if I had known this back then,

02:45.960 --> 02:47.490
I definitely would have...

02:54.590 --> 02:56.800
That's just how your mom is.

02:57.030 --> 02:58.030
Whatever she's going through,

02:58.030 --> 02:59.079
she will only keep it to herself

02:59.079 --> 03:00.480
and not tell anyone else.

03:00.630 --> 03:02.760
She surely won't tell Grandma either.

03:05.530 --> 03:07.300
I want to call my mom.

03:09.340 --> 03:10.010
Go ahead.

03:17.240 --> 03:19.970
Hello, the subscriber you dialed is
powered off.

03:22.840 --> 03:24.240
Her phone is powered off.

03:30.060 --> 03:31.860
Maybe she wants some time alone.

03:32.450 --> 03:33.579
Give her some space.

03:34.430 --> 03:38.900
[The Red Army Boy Who Never Gave Up]

03:55.300 --> 03:56.200
Say it.

03:58.280 --> 04:00.360
Say that it's what you want me to do,

04:02.410 --> 04:03.880
and it's what you wish for.

04:07.670 --> 04:08.400
It's...

04:09.960 --> 04:10.460
It's

04:10.490 --> 04:11.860
what I want you to do.

04:18.279 --> 04:19.690
It's what I wish for.

05:11.260 --> 05:11.900
Who is it?

05:26.430 --> 05:27.270
Ling...

05:29.430 --> 05:31.690
I'm guilty. I'm so sorry.

05:32.740 --> 05:34.230
I'm guilty.

05:34.659 --> 05:35.960
Ling.

05:36.920 --> 05:38.740
Ling, I'm guilty.

05:41.190 --> 05:42.720
I'm a sinner.

05:44.240 --> 05:45.760
I'm guilty.

05:46.480 --> 05:48.360
I owe you an apology.

05:48.800 --> 05:49.950
I'm sorry.

05:49.970 --> 05:51.080
I'm so sorry.

05:51.900 --> 05:52.590
Ling,

05:52.680 --> 05:54.140
I'm guilty.

05:55.230 --> 05:57.210
I'm guilty.

06:02.880 --> 06:05.410
I'm so sorry.

06:06.270 --> 06:09.180
Why didn't you tell me before?

06:09.560 --> 06:11.270
I'm sorry.

06:15.010 --> 06:17.050
I'm sorry.

06:21.780 --> 06:23.460
Sorry, Ling.

06:23.480 --> 06:24.920
I'm so sorry.

06:42.680 --> 06:44.909
I don't even remember

06:45.270 --> 06:47.330
when I bathed you like this last time.

06:53.080 --> 06:54.740
When I was 12.

06:58.040 --> 06:59.140
It's been ages.

07:00.900 --> 07:02.280
It's all my fault.

07:06.980 --> 07:09.380
I was the one who pushed you
into the fire pit

07:10.890 --> 07:13.150
and even saw that beast as my benefactor,

07:14.360 --> 07:16.850
letting him bully you over and over again.

07:21.120 --> 07:22.750
It was the punishment for me.

07:29.240 --> 07:30.360
It was all my fault.

07:33.950 --> 07:35.730
I got Dad killed.

07:37.070 --> 07:38.850
I ruined this family.

07:40.680 --> 07:42.480
It was karma catching up with me.

07:44.190 --> 07:44.680
No.

07:46.560 --> 07:47.960
It's not like that, Ling.

07:48.159 --> 07:49.290
That's not the case.

07:51.260 --> 07:52.460
It was me

07:53.560 --> 07:54.480
who couldn't let go

07:54.480 --> 07:55.810
and dragged you into it.

07:59.430 --> 08:00.580
Actually, I know...

08:03.360 --> 08:04.800
you were not the one to blame

08:04.800 --> 08:06.200
for your dad's accident.

08:06.560 --> 08:07.500
But at that time,

08:08.390 --> 08:09.980
I couldn't get over it.

08:10.390 --> 08:11.680
I couldn't move on.

08:12.040 --> 08:14.370
If I hadn't found someone
to take it out on,

08:14.390 --> 08:16.870
I just couldn't have survived.

08:19.750 --> 08:21.070
I don't deserve to be a mother.

08:21.070 --> 08:22.240
Ling, I don't deserve to be your mom.

08:22.240 --> 08:23.000
Hit me.

08:23.000 --> 08:23.750
Come on.

08:23.750 --> 08:24.480
Hit me.

08:25.310 --> 08:26.430
Hate me.

08:26.430 --> 08:28.600
Just hate me.

08:29.270 --> 08:31.000
I don't deserve to be your mom.

08:47.150 --> 08:48.480
Go home with me

08:49.570 --> 08:51.170
during the Spring Festival.

08:52.270 --> 08:54.530
Let's have your dad laid to rest in peace.

09:07.630 --> 09:09.130
He'll be proud of you,

09:10.120 --> 09:11.410
just like I am.

09:53.200 --> 09:54.660
Why isn't Ding Zhibo in that ward anymore?

09:54.660 --> 09:55.520
Where did he go?

09:55.670 --> 09:56.670
He got discharged long ago.

09:56.670 --> 09:57.870
He left on the day of the accident.

09:57.870 --> 09:58.730
Where did he go?

09:59.960 --> 10:00.960
He went abroad, right?

10:00.960 --> 10:01.750
People like him

10:01.750 --> 10:03.150
would be better off dead.

10:11.480 --> 10:12.120
Sorry,

10:12.550 --> 10:13.720
the subscriber you dialed is

10:13.720 --> 10:15.250
unavailable at the moment.

10:15.360 --> 10:16.690
Please try again later.

10:21.790 --> 10:22.360
Sorry,

10:22.750 --> 10:24.000
the subscriber you dialed is

10:24.000 --> 10:25.530
unavailable at the moment.

10:25.600 --> 10:26.930
Please try again later.

10:47.240 --> 10:47.750
Mom.

10:48.480 --> 10:49.280
You're awake.

10:57.630 --> 10:59.500
There's no food left in the fridge.

10:59.500 --> 11:01.360
Go to the market with me, will you?

11:07.930 --> 11:09.060
It's not your fault.

11:11.630 --> 11:13.550
We should live

11:14.470 --> 11:15.870
without shame.

11:17.240 --> 11:17.770
Let's go.

11:19.540 --> 11:26.230
[Fresh fruit & vegetable]

11:20.120 --> 11:21.480
This shop sells fresh ingredients!

11:21.480 --> 11:22.440
Take a look.

11:22.510 --> 11:23.570
They're all fresh.

11:23.630 --> 11:24.000
Yes.

11:24.000 --> 11:25.720
Are you shopping with your daughter?

11:25.720 --> 11:26.120
Yes.

11:26.600 --> 11:27.630
You're so close.

11:27.630 --> 11:28.560
So sweet.

11:28.670 --> 11:29.440
Yes.

11:29.440 --> 11:30.230
So happy.

11:31.460 --> 11:32.460
Do you want these?

11:34.370 --> 11:35.500
Let's buy one bunch.

11:39.320 --> 11:45.230
[My Farm]

11:45.150 --> 11:46.240
We've got some bamboo shoots.

11:46.240 --> 11:48.040
I'll make the yanduxian for you.

11:48.480 --> 11:49.280
Do you like it?

11:49.360 --> 11:50.150
Anything is fine.

11:50.150 --> 11:51.680
What else do you want to eat?

11:52.390 --> 11:53.570
Don't cook too much.

11:53.630 --> 11:54.570
It's okay.

12:05.190 --> 12:06.180
[Hello, Ms. Yan Ling.
I'm a journalist from Lihai Weekly.

12:06.210 --> 12:08.080
[I'm really hoping
to have an interview with you.]

12:11.200 --> 12:13.110
Just ignore all this crap.

12:22.370 --> 12:23.740
[Luo Liang]

12:24.930 --> 12:26.650
[Luo Liang]

12:29.530 --> 12:33.900
[Springtime for the Wild Lily] [Courage]

12:40.390 --> 12:41.390
No matter what...

12:45.100 --> 12:46.960
I want to say goodbye to you properly.

12:46.960 --> 12:49.320
[Springtime for the Wild Lily]

12:51.960 --> 12:52.550
Yan Ling.

12:54.670 --> 12:55.550
From now on,

12:58.870 --> 13:00.130
I wish you all the best.

13:10.910 --> 13:13.640
When I held you in my arms
in the hospital that day,

13:15.030 --> 13:16.630
I was sure about my feelings.

13:22.550 --> 13:23.270
But later,

13:23.270 --> 13:24.450
I could also feel

13:25.430 --> 13:28.090
you're gradually
distancing yourself from me.

13:28.390 --> 13:28.790
Love

13:30.000 --> 13:31.020
or healing,

13:32.080 --> 13:33.610
we made a different choice.

14:11.140 --> 14:12.400
Thank you for your CDs.

14:14.600 --> 14:15.570
I saw the news.

14:18.410 --> 14:19.230
You're brave.

14:21.150 --> 14:21.880
and awesome.

14:26.400 --> 14:27.760
The last time we met,

14:31.030 --> 14:31.790
you said

14:32.320 --> 14:34.270
we made a different choice.

14:37.410 --> 14:39.150
If I say I made my choice

14:40.370 --> 14:41.900
because I don't deserve it,

14:42.790 --> 14:43.750
can you get it?

14:45.410 --> 14:46.870
When I was still a minor,

14:48.840 --> 14:49.870
I was with a man

14:51.360 --> 14:53.240
old enough to be my dad.

14:55.360 --> 14:56.740
I stuck with him

14:58.750 --> 15:01.260
so as to vent my feelings
of missing and guilt

15:01.600 --> 15:02.540
to my dad.

15:07.600 --> 15:08.400
I feel ashamed

15:10.730 --> 15:13.460
not only because I was
in a relationship with him,

15:16.190 --> 15:17.750
but also because I thought

15:21.240 --> 15:23.300
it was love during the whole process.

15:25.200 --> 15:26.200
From high school,

15:26.390 --> 15:27.270
to university,

15:27.960 --> 15:29.290
and to graduate school,

15:31.030 --> 15:33.830
I had always regarded
this peculiar relationship

15:34.390 --> 15:35.670
as love.

15:37.270 --> 15:39.400
When I felt he was pulling away from me,

15:39.750 --> 15:41.550
I even bought a new dress

15:42.120 --> 15:43.520
and went to meet him in it.

15:44.670 --> 15:45.650
I saw him

15:47.270 --> 15:49.320
with a girl who was 15 or 16 years old,

15:52.080 --> 15:54.640
just like how he was with me
in the beginning.

16:05.640 --> 16:07.840
At that moment, it suddenly dawned on me

16:08.790 --> 16:09.720
that what he felt

16:10.790 --> 16:12.960
for me wasn't some unique love.

16:15.480 --> 16:16.480
I was simply a prey

16:17.360 --> 16:18.560
of his lust

16:19.670 --> 16:21.840
for youth and his quirk.

16:26.590 --> 16:27.920
That wasn't your fault.

16:30.270 --> 16:30.630
No.

16:33.530 --> 16:34.440
I'm terrible.

16:50.240 --> 16:51.480
I got blotto.

16:54.280 --> 16:55.670
Then Lu found me.

16:58.110 --> 16:59.800
He was my most trusted senior.

17:03.150 --> 17:04.510
But I mistook him for...

17:07.240 --> 17:09.300
I bought this dress because of you.

17:10.200 --> 17:12.329
I got dressed up specifically for you!

17:13.510 --> 17:14.109
Yan Ling! Yan Ling!

17:14.109 --> 17:15.550
I'll tear it apart!

17:15.589 --> 17:16.000
Don't...

17:16.000 --> 17:16.800
Don't do this.

17:17.270 --> 17:17.800
Yan Ling!

17:18.720 --> 17:19.300
Yan Ling.

17:19.760 --> 17:20.480
Don't.

17:24.609 --> 17:25.920
I hurt myself.

17:28.240 --> 17:29.350
And I hurt Lu.

17:38.550 --> 17:39.410
I can't believe

17:41.160 --> 17:43.400
I even wore a new dress to meet that guy.

17:44.250 --> 17:46.910
I was like a cheap prostitute,
begging for love.

17:50.370 --> 17:52.430
Don't talk about yourself like that.

17:53.610 --> 17:54.550
It was his fault.

18:04.120 --> 18:05.640
He took advantage of you

18:07.310 --> 18:08.240
at your weakest.

18:11.880 --> 18:14.080
He used your guilt over your dad's death

18:15.240 --> 18:17.920
and your abnormal relationship
with your mother

18:17.920 --> 18:20.120
to become the only pillar in your heart.

18:21.000 --> 18:22.070
If you hadn't told yourself

18:22.070 --> 18:23.000
that it was love,

18:24.270 --> 18:26.200
you couldn't have made it through.

18:32.460 --> 18:34.920
After I got pregnant
with Lu's child, Jiale,

18:37.180 --> 18:38.080
I thought

18:38.240 --> 18:39.970
I had finally gotten rid of him.

18:42.310 --> 18:43.840
I took a year off from school

18:44.030 --> 18:45.360
and gave birth to Jiale.

18:46.920 --> 18:48.180
Then I went on to do a PhD

18:49.460 --> 18:51.060
and stayed to work at school.

18:52.880 --> 18:54.020
I told myself

18:54.200 --> 18:55.690
I wanted to start over.

18:57.640 --> 18:59.100
I wanted to be a good mother

19:00.830 --> 19:01.920
and a good teacher.

19:03.160 --> 19:04.690
I wanted to be a good person.

19:13.750 --> 19:14.510
In my eyes,

19:16.230 --> 19:17.830
you're always a good person.

19:33.640 --> 19:34.750
In order to pass

19:34.750 --> 19:36.210
the core assessment of PUA

19:36.240 --> 19:37.370
to get the evidence,

19:38.550 --> 19:39.920
I filmed a video with Lu.

19:45.200 --> 19:46.260
That kind of video?

19:48.270 --> 19:49.670
Of course, it's not true.

19:53.790 --> 19:55.710
If it works

19:57.640 --> 19:59.170
and can help avenge Leilei,

20:00.590 --> 20:01.720
I'm willing to do it.

20:16.950 --> 20:18.490
Is this your whole story?

20:23.020 --> 20:24.590
Why did you come to me today?

20:27.790 --> 20:29.320
Why did you tell me all this?

20:36.510 --> 20:37.770
I've never

20:38.790 --> 20:40.650
ever been in a real relationship.

20:43.590 --> 20:45.740
I can't even trust my own feelings

20:47.130 --> 20:48.520
or know what love is.

20:53.920 --> 20:55.380
But after I met you,

20:57.920 --> 20:59.580
I really wanted to tell you...

21:04.070 --> 21:05.400
Don't leave me.

21:07.550 --> 21:09.000
Don't leave me alone.

21:12.960 --> 21:14.600
Don't go!

21:14.880 --> 21:16.880
Don't leave me!

21:17.350 --> 21:19.790
Don't leave me alone again!

21:51.240 --> 21:52.520
You've suffered.

21:56.880 --> 21:57.950
Poor thing.

22:21.310 --> 22:22.220
I love you.

23:11.470 --> 23:12.700
I never knew

23:13.950 --> 23:15.700
I could be so happy.

23:17.070 --> 23:18.020
Me, too.

23:44.850 --> 23:45.710
Hello, Ms. Yan.

23:57.480 --> 23:58.110
Yan Ling!

23:59.680 --> 24:00.440
Mrs. Feng.

24:03.480 --> 24:06.000
Dear, you've suffered.

24:06.590 --> 24:08.920
How have you been through all these years?

24:10.030 --> 24:10.560
Luckily,

24:11.120 --> 24:12.160
I'm still alive.

24:12.330 --> 24:13.960
I know there are bad guys

24:13.960 --> 24:15.210
and jerks like this in the world.

24:15.210 --> 24:16.270
But I didn't expect

24:16.310 --> 24:16.880
they could...

24:16.880 --> 24:18.680
they could really be this awful.

24:18.750 --> 24:20.030
He should go to hell.

24:20.590 --> 24:21.370
Ms. Yan.

24:22.510 --> 24:23.310
Director Lin.

24:25.070 --> 24:26.310
Come to my office.

24:27.680 --> 24:28.200
Oh, and I'll

24:28.200 --> 24:29.730
go to the institute office.

24:32.070 --> 24:32.730
Have a seat.

24:35.770 --> 24:36.590
I'm sorry.

24:36.780 --> 24:37.200
Look.

24:37.920 --> 24:39.180
My room is a total mess.

24:42.270 --> 24:44.000
Have a bottle of water, please.

24:44.510 --> 24:45.220
Thank you.

24:49.880 --> 24:50.600
Sorry,

24:51.590 --> 24:52.470
I didn't know

24:53.030 --> 24:54.960
something like that had happened.

24:55.670 --> 24:56.510
Back then,

24:57.160 --> 24:58.750
the school and I

24:58.750 --> 25:00.880
even asked you to go and talk to Ding...

25:01.790 --> 25:02.850
I'm really sorry,

25:02.960 --> 25:03.490
Yan Ling.

25:04.870 --> 25:06.850
It's not on you or the school.

25:08.510 --> 25:09.110
But

25:09.550 --> 25:11.010
about the scholarship...

25:11.880 --> 25:13.680
We definitely can't collaborate

25:13.680 --> 25:15.510
with Oceanvision International
for the scholarship now.

25:15.510 --> 25:16.570
But the school said

25:17.220 --> 25:19.110
we've already selected the candidates,

25:19.110 --> 25:20.600
and we can't let the students down.

25:20.600 --> 25:21.260
So,

25:21.350 --> 25:22.260
it will be paid

25:22.680 --> 25:24.010
by the school this time.

25:25.700 --> 25:26.510
I'm sorry.

25:27.550 --> 25:28.110
No matter what,

25:28.110 --> 25:29.880
you're not the one to say sorry.

25:30.070 --> 25:31.800
The one who should apologize is

25:31.920 --> 25:33.680
the one who did evil.

25:34.420 --> 25:35.130
However,

25:35.350 --> 25:37.130
you should be mentally prepared.

25:37.130 --> 25:37.700
Look.

25:38.440 --> 25:40.920
Oceanvision International
just issued a statement,

25:40.920 --> 25:42.200
denied everything,

25:43.590 --> 25:45.190
and even said they'd sue you.

25:46.840 --> 25:48.380
The media's been

25:48.530 --> 25:49.930
swarming into the school

25:50.030 --> 25:51.030
the past few days.

25:51.390 --> 25:54.560
We didn't even get so many people here
for the school anniversary.

25:54.560 --> 25:55.410
I saw it.

25:56.550 --> 25:58.080
What should come will come.

26:00.550 --> 26:01.070
By the way,

26:01.070 --> 26:01.960
the students

26:02.110 --> 26:03.400
will have their thesis defense later.

26:03.400 --> 26:04.800
Go cheer on your class.

26:06.420 --> 26:06.970
Got it?

26:10.070 --> 26:11.270
Thank you, Director.

26:11.960 --> 26:12.890
Thank you.

26:30.790 --> 26:32.030
Hello, judges.

26:32.030 --> 26:33.040
I'm Li Changning.

26:33.240 --> 26:35.750
My student ID is 151601043.

26:36.160 --> 26:37.270
My thesis title is

26:37.000 --> 26:37.890
[Research on a New Method
for Multi-Band Wave Energy Capture]

26:37.270 --> 26:39.240
"Research on a New Method
for Multi-Band Wave Energy Capture

26:37.920 --> 26:38.560
[And Its Directional Spectrum Analysis]

26:39.240 --> 26:41.720
and Its Directional Spectrum Analysis."

26:41.880 --> 26:43.070
-My thesis focuses
-Yan Ling.

26:43.070 --> 26:44.640
-Someone is looking for you.
-on the wave theory spectra

26:44.640 --> 26:46.110
and numerical methods

26:46.110 --> 26:48.270
for simulating waves
based on the spectrum.

26:48.270 --> 26:51.130
The ocean is
the most crucial water system on Earth.

26:51.680 --> 26:53.750
It affects the global climate
and environment.

26:53.750 --> 26:55.410
To accurately comprehend...

27:01.240 --> 27:02.440
What brings you here?

27:03.100 --> 27:06.360
I don't have much work to do
at the hospital this afternoon.

27:06.360 --> 27:07.170
I missed you.

27:09.570 --> 27:11.570
And I'm also a bit worried about you.

27:12.270 --> 27:15.200
After all, you're
kind of in the spotlight right now.

27:16.830 --> 27:18.030
I'm not that fragile.

27:19.530 --> 27:20.780
I know you're tough.

27:22.940 --> 27:24.850
Li Changning is having her thesis defense.

27:24.850 --> 27:25.430
Really?

27:26.240 --> 27:27.480
Her thesis is solid.

27:27.530 --> 27:28.790
I'm not worried at all.

27:31.240 --> 27:32.370
I'm going in.

27:32.510 --> 27:33.170
Wait for me.

27:33.310 --> 27:35.160
Let's have dinner together after this.

27:35.160 --> 27:35.510
Okay.

27:39.110 --> 27:39.840
Yan Ling.

27:46.540 --> 27:48.140
I don't want to wait anymore.

27:52.110 --> 27:53.170
Let's get married.

28:18.590 --> 28:20.520
[Certificate Holder, Yan Ling]

28:20.650 --> 28:21.810
Congratulations on your marriage.

28:21.810 --> 28:22.850
Wish you a lifetime of happiness together.

28:22.030 --> 28:25.450
[Certificate Holder, Yan Ling]

28:35.160 --> 28:35.690
Alright.

28:36.290 --> 28:36.830
Lu.

28:38.200 --> 28:39.240
I want to tell you

28:40.110 --> 28:41.170
that Luo Liang and I

28:41.270 --> 28:42.470
got married legally.

28:43.350 --> 28:44.260
I know.

28:44.880 --> 28:45.940
Jiale told me that.

28:47.070 --> 28:48.320
Well...

28:48.340 --> 28:50.320
Um... Dr. Luo is quite a nice guy.

28:51.790 --> 28:52.850
Congratulations.

28:53.240 --> 28:55.040
I've always wanted to apologize

28:55.800 --> 28:57.640
to you for what happened back then.

28:57.640 --> 28:58.690
Don't say that.

29:00.200 --> 29:02.000
You should have told me earlier.

29:02.270 --> 29:03.310
If I had known that,

29:03.310 --> 29:05.270
I wouldn't have left you alone to face it.

29:05.270 --> 29:07.530
I'd definitely have stayed by your side.

29:08.310 --> 29:08.710
Not...

29:08.920 --> 29:10.860
N-Not as your boyfriend,

29:11.000 --> 29:11.790
but as your friend.

29:11.790 --> 29:12.850
Just pure friends.

29:14.110 --> 29:15.440
I didn't lose anything.

29:16.000 --> 29:17.150
I've even got a son.

29:19.960 --> 29:20.690
Give me a hug.

29:21.000 --> 29:22.000
So disgusting.

29:22.390 --> 29:23.720
Are you out of your mind?

29:24.310 --> 29:27.700
I must hug you today!

29:27.790 --> 29:28.980
You little brat.

29:30.000 --> 29:30.400
Get in.

29:30.770 --> 29:31.300
Let's go.

29:46.510 --> 29:48.040
Are you still busy, Chubby?

29:48.740 --> 29:50.030
You bought so many sachima?

29:50.030 --> 29:50.830
I'll have one.

29:52.160 --> 29:52.590
Stop.

29:54.680 --> 29:55.170
What?

29:55.200 --> 29:56.640
Is it specifically for a contributor?

29:56.640 --> 29:59.270
You weren't this protective
of your food before.

29:59.270 --> 30:00.070
It's not food.

30:00.830 --> 30:01.690
It's all clues.

30:02.640 --> 30:03.960
Clues? What clues?

30:06.700 --> 30:08.400
I'm looking for the exact type of sachima

30:08.400 --> 30:10.000
that Mister brought the girls

30:10.000 --> 30:11.060
to eat.

30:11.400 --> 30:12.920
You're still investigating that pervert?

30:12.920 --> 30:14.580
Are you addicted to being a hero?

30:14.580 --> 30:15.640
Didn't Chief Hu say

30:16.160 --> 30:17.000
For us police,

30:17.000 --> 30:17.830
the greatest expectation is

30:17.830 --> 30:19.000
not to be heroes,

30:19.200 --> 30:19.830
but to see the days

30:19.830 --> 30:21.490
pass by peacefully and safely

30:21.640 --> 30:22.840
without any trouble.

30:25.460 --> 30:28.350
"I specifically invited her
to take the last ferry.

30:28.960 --> 30:31.960
When we got off, there were
no buses, no underground trains.

30:31.960 --> 30:34.240
I said it was God who let her stay
for one night,

30:34.240 --> 30:35.830
so I could treat her

30:35.830 --> 30:38.200
to a one-of-a-kind delicacy
in the world tomorrow.

30:38.200 --> 30:39.230
After that night,

30:40.400 --> 30:41.960
she fell for me completely

30:42.070 --> 30:43.270
and did whatever I said,

30:43.270 --> 30:45.850
until she hung herself under the banyan.

30:45.920 --> 30:48.050
The last words she left were

30:48.200 --> 30:49.350
that she hoped

30:49.550 --> 30:50.880
she'd be worthy of being

30:51.110 --> 30:52.510
with me in the next life."

30:53.880 --> 30:55.310
This novel is well written.

30:55.310 --> 30:56.160
What novel?

30:56.830 --> 30:58.640
Whose novel could be so real

30:58.640 --> 30:59.390
and vivid?

30:59.860 --> 31:00.640
If you're writing a novel,

31:00.640 --> 31:02.240
will you even specifically find
a photo of sachima

31:02.240 --> 31:03.110
to put in it?

31:03.270 --> 31:04.200
Novel?

31:04.310 --> 31:05.910
Alright, let me check it out.

31:06.640 --> 31:07.240
Let me see.

31:12.620 --> 31:14.540
[Experimental Diary:
White Mice Experiment 1, the Snow Queen]

31:14.690 --> 31:15.310
[Experimental Diary:
White Mice Experiment 2]

31:15.340 --> 31:15.910
[Edward Scissorhands, Written by Mister]

31:16.440 --> 31:17.970
He's quite good at writing.

31:18.000 --> 31:18.270
Well...

31:18.270 --> 31:20.480
If he drops a novel,
I'll definitely read it.

31:20.480 --> 31:22.570
I told you it's not a novel.

31:22.640 --> 31:23.440
It's not.

31:24.830 --> 31:25.290
Come on.

31:26.180 --> 31:27.580
Take a look at this, then.

31:28.030 --> 31:29.930
Look at this Snow Queen chapter.

31:29.960 --> 31:30.960
Just by talking,

31:31.070 --> 31:33.160
he made a beauty fall so hard for him

31:33.270 --> 31:34.240
that she even killed herself.

31:34.240 --> 31:35.590
Apparently, he must be a perverted writer

31:35.590 --> 31:36.720
who has nowhere
to project his shady desires,

31:36.720 --> 31:38.480
writing things to satisfy
his own fantasies.

31:38.480 --> 31:38.880
Listen,

31:38.880 --> 31:40.010
just think about it.

31:40.270 --> 31:41.790
If being in a relationship
could kill people,

31:41.540 --> 31:42.220
[I'll follow your lead.]

31:41.790 --> 31:43.000
humans on Earth
would've long been extinct.

31:42.240 --> 31:43.320
[Hope I can learn
one-tenth of your skill.]

31:45.290 --> 31:46.440
I told you not to eat it,

31:46.440 --> 31:47.640
didn't I?

31:47.750 --> 31:49.010
Just let me grab a bite.

31:50.000 --> 31:50.790
Besides, it's

31:50.790 --> 31:52.460
not almond sachima, I think.

31:54.190 --> 31:54.850
What "ond"?

31:55.000 --> 31:56.200
Almond sachima.

31:56.440 --> 31:59.510
It's a unique specialty
of Cuiying Pavilion in Shenchuan.

31:59.510 --> 32:00.370
How do you know?

32:03.410 --> 32:04.570
Look, Cuiying Pavilion.

32:04.570 --> 32:05.700
I'm from Shenchuan.

32:06.200 --> 32:07.880
This place is called Cuiying Pavilion?

32:07.880 --> 32:08.350
Yes.

32:13.710 --> 32:15.020
[Cuiying Pavilion]

32:17.400 --> 32:18.080
[Welcome to Cuiying Pavilion, Shenchuan]

32:18.570 --> 32:19.910
[Extraordinary dining experience]

32:22.420 --> 32:24.780
[Extraordinary dining experience]

32:22.830 --> 32:24.560
It is indeed Cuiying Pavilion.

32:26.180 --> 32:28.180
I've got to pay a visit to Shenchuan.

32:31.420 --> 32:32.740
Impressive, Liu!

32:33.270 --> 32:34.130
What's up, bro?

32:35.270 --> 32:35.860
Eat it.

32:36.070 --> 32:37.530
It's all yours. Eat it all.

32:38.160 --> 32:39.500
So you finally get it, bro.

32:39.500 --> 32:39.950
Okay.

32:41.440 --> 32:45.790
[Shenchuan]

32:44.480 --> 32:46.320
You're asking the right person.

32:45.810 --> 32:52.070
[Thriving Aura]

32:46.350 --> 32:48.370
I've been here
since the opening of this shop.

32:48.370 --> 32:50.900
I've been working here
for more than 10 years.

32:51.070 --> 32:52.400
The one who was in our business

32:52.400 --> 32:54.550
and committed suicide under the banyan.

32:54.550 --> 32:56.100
It must be her.

32:56.680 --> 32:57.930
Mr. Tony, right?

32:59.200 --> 33:01.930
Are you sure her name is Wei Zhihua?

33:02.510 --> 33:04.830
Yes, Zhihua.

33:05.160 --> 33:07.030
I remember it was 2013

33:07.440 --> 33:09.030
when she ran away.

33:09.270 --> 33:10.590
A host of customers couldn't find her

33:10.590 --> 33:12.720
and came to the shop to ask for refunds.

33:12.960 --> 33:14.180
What guests?

33:14.640 --> 33:16.610
She was so pretty.

33:16.640 --> 33:17.890
Don't you get it?

33:18.070 --> 33:19.430
You know, men.

33:19.720 --> 33:21.270
Doesn't she have a boyfriend?'

33:21.270 --> 33:22.400
What is a boyfriend?

33:23.270 --> 33:25.530
If everyone who slept with her
counted as one,

33:25.530 --> 33:27.160
you'd need to find a whole lot of people.

33:27.160 --> 33:29.330
Who knew she would commit suicide?

33:29.960 --> 33:31.620
A beautiful woman died young.

33:32.590 --> 33:33.270
Tony,

33:33.610 --> 33:34.340
could you...

33:34.590 --> 33:35.720
Could you help me confirm

33:35.720 --> 33:36.070
if she...

33:36.070 --> 33:37.130
if she had this kind

33:37.920 --> 33:39.120
of tattoo on her body?

33:43.330 --> 33:45.280
No, I didn't see this.

33:45.790 --> 33:47.900
Anyway, there was no tattoo
on the skin she showed.

33:47.900 --> 33:49.110
As for the private areas,

33:49.110 --> 33:50.270
I don't know, either.

33:50.270 --> 33:52.070
I never slept with her, right?

33:55.640 --> 33:56.240
By the way,

33:56.790 --> 33:58.070
she has an older brother

33:58.070 --> 33:59.200
who also lives in Shenchuan.

33:59.200 --> 34:01.000
I remember his name is Xiang.

34:02.270 --> 34:04.330
Do you have his contact information?

34:06.000 --> 34:06.590
Handsome,

34:06.590 --> 34:08.510
is there a toilet seller called...

34:08.510 --> 34:09.239
I don't know.

34:11.280 --> 34:11.860
Sir,

34:12.000 --> 34:14.429
is there a toilet seller named Xiang?

34:17.480 --> 34:17.880
Sir.

34:19.480 --> 34:20.800
Check out these toilets.

34:20.800 --> 34:22.030
All my goods are from Foshan.

34:22.030 --> 34:22.870
Wei Xiang?

34:23.469 --> 34:23.800
Yes.

34:24.030 --> 34:24.840
They all call me Xiang.

34:24.840 --> 34:27.639
You have a younger sister
named Wei Zhihua, right?

34:30.290 --> 34:31.889
My sister was bad-tempered.

34:32.150 --> 34:33.150
She didn't like me nagging her.

34:33.150 --> 34:35.210
I couldn't see her all year round.

34:35.360 --> 34:37.420
She was not even home
for the New Year.

34:37.440 --> 34:38.400
We could see neither her

34:38.400 --> 34:39.280
nor her money.

34:39.889 --> 34:40.670
My parents just act

34:40.670 --> 34:42.330
like they never had this girl.

34:42.670 --> 34:44.800
So what happened back then?

34:44.800 --> 34:47.139
Why did she suddenly commit suicide?

34:47.880 --> 34:49.210
I know nothing about it.

34:49.550 --> 34:51.070
The year she committed suicide,
I called her

34:51.070 --> 34:52.600
before the Spring Festival

34:54.550 --> 34:55.880
and introduced her to my colleague.

34:55.880 --> 34:56.949
I thought a girl

34:57.030 --> 34:58.510
should get married early and have a baby

34:58.510 --> 34:59.710
to live a stable life.

35:01.630 --> 35:03.070
She scolded me on the phone again.

35:03.070 --> 35:04.180
I got upset, too.

35:04.360 --> 35:05.420
So we lost contact.

35:05.920 --> 35:07.880
A few months later,
the police found me and said

35:07.880 --> 35:09.940
something had happened
to my sister.

35:14.920 --> 35:17.360
Do you have her previous photos

35:17.360 --> 35:18.570
or videos?

35:19.150 --> 35:21.190
Maybe you can take a look

35:21.400 --> 35:22.200
at her QQ blog.

35:23.190 --> 35:24.000
After she died,

35:24.000 --> 35:25.600
I don't know how to handle it.

35:25.670 --> 35:27.110
My sister was actually quite pretty.

35:27.110 --> 35:27.890
My colleague

35:27.920 --> 35:28.920
took a fancy to her

35:28.920 --> 35:30.320
just because he saw her photos.

35:30.320 --> 35:31.030
I see.

35:32.070 --> 35:32.480
Okay.

35:32.590 --> 35:33.820
Two, three, nine...

35:34.400 --> 35:36.280
Okay, okay. Thank you.

35:42.930 --> 35:45.510
[Memory of Youth]

35:51.140 --> 35:52.760
[Photo albums]

35:52.810 --> 35:53.410
[Verification question]

35:53.430 --> 35:54.910
[Question: The best day]

36:09.670 --> 36:12.710
[Question: The best day]

36:15.200 --> 36:17.070
[The happiest day]

36:28.810 --> 36:33.260
[Support group
for victims of romance fraud]

36:28.960 --> 36:30.630
I've had trouble
falling asleep for months.

36:30.630 --> 36:32.290
I'm losing almost all my hair.

36:32.510 --> 36:35.070
I can't stop regretting
how stupid I was back then.

36:35.070 --> 36:37.190
I gave her all the money
for my mom's medical expenses.

36:37.190 --> 36:38.230
Now I see my mom...

36:38.440 --> 36:40.380
There are way too many morons

36:40.540 --> 36:41.920
for liars to cheat.

36:42.320 --> 36:44.480
Every day, I wish I could wake up
and find out

36:44.480 --> 36:45.880
this is all just a dream.

36:47.280 --> 36:48.210
Excuse me,

36:48.710 --> 36:50.710
has anyone seen this tattoo before?

36:50.840 --> 36:51.730
No.

36:51.840 --> 36:53.240
What's going on with you?

36:53.510 --> 36:54.510
It's not about me.

36:54.510 --> 36:55.770
It was my elder sister.

36:56.070 --> 36:57.980
She jumped off a building at Chengyu Gym

36:57.980 --> 36:59.050
8 years ago.

36:59.140 --> 37:05.010
[Mumu]

36:59.760 --> 37:01.160
Not until she passed away

37:01.320 --> 37:02.000
did we find

37:02.000 --> 37:03.360
this tattoo on her body.

37:05.670 --> 37:06.810
Where are you from?

37:06.920 --> 37:07.920
Eight years? That was a long time ago.

37:07.920 --> 37:09.380
Chengyu Gym?

37:10.000 --> 37:11.880
-Isn't romance baiting conducted online?
-Eight years ago...

37:11.880 --> 37:13.030
Did your sister get scammed out of money?

37:13.030 --> 37:14.320
-Why did she commit suicide?
-We're from Bingyuan.

37:14.320 --> 37:14.960
Bingyuan?

37:17.750 --> 37:19.600
[Mumu]

37:19.700 --> 37:21.420
[Add friend]

37:21.070 --> 37:21.740
Hello.

37:21.790 --> 37:25.740
[Send a friend request]

37:21.880 --> 37:22.880
I'm from Chengyu.

37:23.280 --> 37:25.070
Was your sister a skater?

37:25.510 --> 37:27.890
I remember your sister's suicide was

37:25.880 --> 37:26.860
[Add friend]

37:26.940 --> 37:28.060
[Sending]

37:27.960 --> 37:29.240
big news in Chengyu.

37:48.260 --> 37:49.670
[Bingyuan City]

37:53.670 --> 37:55.070
My sister could already skate

37:55.070 --> 37:56.470
when she learned to walk.

37:56.710 --> 37:59.480
She had been fond of Katarina
since she was little.

37:59.480 --> 38:01.000
She wanted to become an athlete

38:01.000 --> 38:03.130
remembered by everyone just like her.

38:03.440 --> 38:04.590
For this goal,

38:05.140 --> 38:06.940
she almost lived at the ice rink.

38:07.760 --> 38:09.380
I saw her performance

38:10.110 --> 38:12.370
in the Asian Open Figure Skating Trophy.

38:13.150 --> 38:14.080
She was amazing.

38:15.510 --> 38:16.590
But in that game,

38:18.280 --> 38:19.330
I remember she...

38:19.800 --> 38:21.020
But in that game,

38:21.280 --> 38:22.080
she fell down.

38:28.230 --> 38:29.830
And she never stood up again.

38:31.480 --> 38:32.370
So this was

38:32.800 --> 38:33.030
why

38:33.030 --> 38:34.150
she chose...

38:35.110 --> 38:37.170
My sister was not that kind of person.

38:37.400 --> 38:38.460
After she got hurt,

38:38.960 --> 38:41.360
she worked really hard
on her rehabilitation

38:41.360 --> 38:42.620
and never gave up hope.

38:44.110 --> 38:45.080
Then why did that

38:45.230 --> 38:45.710
happen?

38:48.590 --> 38:49.690
I suspect...

38:51.400 --> 38:53.860
it was her boyfriend
who forced her to death.

38:54.320 --> 38:56.250
Her boyfriend forced her to death?

39:01.400 --> 39:02.190
No one

39:02.920 --> 39:05.180
except me knows
that my sister was dating

39:05.920 --> 39:07.850
a mysterious boyfriend secretly.

39:09.110 --> 39:10.950
But I was too young at that time.

39:11.760 --> 39:13.890
I didn't get to see that man many times.

39:14.280 --> 39:16.410
So I don't remember what he looks like.

39:18.230 --> 39:19.460
But my sister

39:20.710 --> 39:21.840
got a tattoo for him.

39:22.440 --> 39:24.900
You mean the one you posted
in the group chat?

39:33.190 --> 39:34.070
I only remember

39:34.070 --> 39:35.550
when my sister was in that relationship,

39:35.550 --> 39:36.630
she was in agony

39:37.070 --> 39:38.270
and crying every day.

39:38.670 --> 39:39.670
But I never thought

39:39.670 --> 39:42.360
my sister's death
would have something to do with him.

39:42.360 --> 39:43.630
Until I saw in the news

39:44.110 --> 39:45.320
the tattoo and mark

39:45.320 --> 39:46.780
mentioned in PUA classes.

39:47.710 --> 39:49.640
So I hurried to join the chat group.

39:51.000 --> 39:51.960
I also found this

39:53.230 --> 39:53.800
and this.

40:05.710 --> 40:06.620
Can you send

40:06.790 --> 40:07.910
these photos to me?

40:10.800 --> 40:15.290
[The Dark Romance]

40:21.730 --> 40:23.250
Stay away from my husband.

40:27.630 --> 40:28.880
Who is that guy?

40:28.880 --> 40:30.150
How could she do that?

40:30.150 --> 40:30.610
Look...

40:30.670 --> 40:32.550
Look at the coffee all over your clothes.

40:32.550 --> 40:34.190
You didn't get burned, did you?

40:34.190 --> 40:34.620
Hey.

40:34.670 --> 40:36.360
She was talking nonsense

40:36.360 --> 40:37.000
and full of crap.

40:37.000 --> 40:38.920
She talked with zero accountability.

40:38.920 --> 40:39.680
Listen,

40:39.710 --> 40:41.000
I won't let her get away with this.

40:41.000 --> 40:41.960
Which class is she in?

40:41.960 --> 40:43.550
I'll definitely go talk to her later.

40:43.550 --> 40:44.150
I'll go...

40:47.190 --> 40:48.760
You're my girlfriend now.

40:48.760 --> 40:50.880
I can't let you suffer this grievance.

40:50.880 --> 40:53.080
I'll definitely go have a word with her.

41:03.110 --> 41:04.570
She was telling the truth.

41:10.110 --> 41:12.080
It was my fault that night.

41:13.670 --> 41:14.730
It was all my fault.

41:19.360 --> 41:21.560
I can't be considered your girlfriend.

41:22.550 --> 41:24.210
Don't worry about me anymore.

41:25.400 --> 41:26.510
And don't come to find me again.

41:26.510 --> 41:27.550
No, no.

41:29.400 --> 41:30.730
Can you stop it, please?

41:33.030 --> 41:35.190
Just pretend nothing ever happened.

41:37.110 --> 41:37.710
I'm sorry.

41:37.710 --> 41:38.550
It's all my fault.

41:38.550 --> 41:39.440
Wait, you...

41:39.440 --> 41:40.960
How could I pretend it never happened?

41:40.960 --> 41:41.410
You...

41:43.230 --> 41:44.280
You...

41:44.280 --> 41:45.150
What do you take me for?

41:45.150 --> 41:45.630
I...

41:45.630 --> 41:47.160
Am I a Band-Aid?

41:48.150 --> 41:48.830
I'm sorry.

41:49.480 --> 41:49.960
Sorry.
